---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Terms & Conditions - Bodhic AI">
    <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);">Terms & Conditions</h1>
        <div style="color: var(--body); line-height: 1.8; font-size: 16px;">
            <p>Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>
            <h3 style="color: var(--ink); margin-top: var(--space-xl);">1. Acceptance of Terms</h3>
            <p>By accessing and using Bodhic AI, you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. If you disagree with any part of the terms, you may not access the service.</p>
            <h3 style="color: var(--ink); margin-top: var(--space-xl);">2. Marketplace Rules</h3>
            <p>Bodhic AI is a marketplace for AI agent skills and prompts. Sellers must hold the intellectual property rights to the items they upload. Buyers receive a non-exclusive license to use the purchased digital goods.</p>
            <h3 style="color: var(--ink); margin-top: var(--space-xl);">3. Security & Liability</h3>
            <p>While Bodhic AI performs automated security scans on uploaded artifacts, buyers are responsible for safely utilizing the provided code or prompts in their environments. Bodhic AI shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages resulting from the use of any marketplace item.</p>
            <h3 style="color: var(--ink); margin-top: var(--space-xl);">4. Governing Law</h3>
            <p>These terms shall be governed and construed in accordance with the laws of India, without regard to its conflict of law provisions.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
